Bulletin,is,a,developer,and,supplier,of,product,and,service,for,messaging,SMS,Text,between,mobile,devices,and,web,applications,The,Bulletin,Messenger,API,is,a,simple,RESTful,SMS,API,allowing,developers,to,send,SMS,messages,to,their,application,users,It,also,envelops,worldwide,coverage,and,pricing,rates,from,as,low,as,c,per,message,The,Bulletin,API,is,REST,based,and,uses,an,HTTP,interface